<p>Bamboo: Tool for build and automated deployement. 
At schoology: used for build mostly.</p>

<h5 id="stages-and-tasks">Stages and Tasks</h5>
<p>Each stage has set of tasks. Different types of tests like unit tests, UI Tests,
Integration tests etc.</p>

